### Create URL (requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/urls
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "original_url": "https://example.com/very/long/url/that/needs/to/be/shortened",
  "short_code": "abc123",
  "expires_at": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

### Create URL without custom short code
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/urls
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "original_url": "https://github.com/golang/go"
}

### Create URL without authentication (should fail)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/urls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "original_url": "https://example.com/test"
}
